{"type": "article", "id": 17836, "title": "水壶 or 高脚杯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-20T07:10:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115208NcQ40KzwanOu6CJm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个可以上下拧开的水壶，底座上的大圆盖拧下来可以转到壶嘴的盖子上，变成一个高脚杯。此外，能打开的底座也很方便清洗。水壶表面像灰色的大理石，带给水壶一种典雅的气质，它其实用了两层不锈钢，有很好的保温效果。产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/367705503/the-pint-a-canteen-that-converts-to-a-cup\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115205r6USHwFZif5PhYna.gif\" width=\"518\" height=\"389\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75096525\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115206o2mOLRKG1rlWtnF4.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"587\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115207TJZmHBl5PdSYAMyI.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"588\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115207JrxsOy8bhc9CKlnU.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"588\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}